A small program for twiddling bits inside your Amiga.

        @{"Introduction" link "INTRODUCTION"}--what @{i}Knobs@{ui} does
        @{"Instructions" link "INSTRUCTIONS"}--how to make it do it

        @{"Program history" link "HISTORY"}
